site/index.html:314:                Track Your <span class="gradient-text">Claude.ai</span> Usage
site/index.html:319:                Keep track of your Claude.ai plan usage at a glance. A lightweight macOS menu bar app for power users.
site/index.html:354:                <p class="text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 text-lg max-w-2xl mx-auto">Powerful features designed for Claude.ai power users who want complete visibility into their usage.</p>
site/index.html:367:                    <p class="text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">Track your 5-hour session limits, 7-day weekly usage, and Sonnet-specific limits in real-time. Never get caught off guard by hitting your limits.</p>
site/index.html:378:                    <p class="text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">Color-coded gauge icon in your menu bar. Green for safe, yellow for warning, red for critical - see your status at a glance.</p>
site/index.html:400:                    <p class="text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">Automatic usage updates every 1, 5, or 10 minutes. Set it and forget it - your usage data is always up to date.</p>
site/index.html:411:                    <p class="text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">Export usage data as JSON for integration with external tools, scripts, and dashboards (e.g. Claude Code statusline).</p>
site/index.html:422:                    <p class="text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">Session keys are encrypted and stored securely in the macOS Keychain. Your credentials never leave your machine.</p>
